    "name": "斗食战酱",
    "steam_appid": 2141280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>烹饪、指挥、竞技。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《斗食战酱》是一款叙事性十足的美食精灵战斗游戏，融合了日式角色扮演冒险、烹饪小游戏和 6 对 6 的回合制战斗。跟随七位战斗厨师的故事，参与并角逐斗瘦场冠军，以及在肉鸽回合锦标赛模式中观察他们的关系（以及你的技能）是如何发生变化的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/3a91b53a14aca5c86be2136f408e0c0c.poster.avif?t=1771580853\" width=612 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/3a91b53a14aca5c86be2136f408e0c0c.webm?t=1771580853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创造你的美食精灵？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >烹饪一口大小的食物，将食材切碎、煮沸、烘烤和煎炸，使其达到最佳战斗状态。每一轮都是扩充队伍或将现有的美食战士进化和强化的机会！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/06935cb9054b25ae8505459eeb0fa1e8.poster.avif?t=1771580853\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/06935cb9054b25ae8505459eeb0fa1e8.webm?t=1771580853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>指挥你的食物！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装盘完毕后，你可以在最多 6 对 6 的回合制战斗中，指挥你的美食精灵进行战斗！从超过 65 个手绘的美食角斗士技能和协同战斗效果中，打造属于你的独家策略和连击战斗风格。解锁厨师的隐藏力量和调味料，体验更多惊喜。你有能力征服斗瘦场吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/44acaae1d74f8e8d22a12b8ea23e9f60.poster.avif?t=1771580853\" width=613 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/44acaae1d74f8e8d22a12b8ea23e9f60.webm?t=1771580853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择你的战斗厨师</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >七个关于烹饪、冲突和同情的故事将引领你走向斗瘦场：爱玩谐音梗的蛋农、只会说一种语言的芬兰烘焙师（与他最好的朋友），以及至少一位不胜不归的秘密特工。他们将在此大显厨艺，或清算旧恩怨，或成为好朋友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/8cda26890eebc27ca1f1dc49566063dc.poster.avif?t=1771580853\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/8cda26890eebc27ca1f1dc49566063dc.webm?t=1771580853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中你会了解每个角色的烹饪特长，然后踏上由美食锦标赛引发的日式角色扮演冒险之旅。 美食角斗士将探索烹饪和美食以外的故事，游戏以精美的像素动画和漫威及 DC 艺术家罗西·坎佩的漫画片段为特色，带您探索烹饪和美食的意义。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/82d5602af0dc13beb32adc2faf0c3b49.poster.avif?t=1771580853\" width=613 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/82d5602af0dc13beb32adc2faf0c3b49.webm?t=1771580853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与好友对战（使用各自的美食精灵）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在线多人游戏，与好友一较高低，比拼你的厨艺或者运用你的战斗能力，在排行榜上一较高低，成为全球最强的战斗厨师！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/9506102fc523f098cb5dae15376c16bc.poster.avif?t=1771580853\" width=612 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/9506102fc523f098cb5dae15376c16bc.webm?t=1771580853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>掌控菜单</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事仍在继续，斗瘦场内的紧张刺激程度不断升级！你将挑战一系列难度递增的战斗，并通过调味器、可解锁的增强模块以及特殊能力和外观来检验你的厨艺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/491c07b9a924cd767d3d48fae4360252.poster.avif?t=1771580853\" width=612 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/491c07b9a924cd767d3d48fae4360252.webm?t=1771580853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>美食角斗士</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 个相互交织的厨师间的故事，构成了一场日式角色扮演冒险之旅</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一对一在线多人对战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有超过65 个美食角斗士，均以精美的像素画风精心呈现，另有隐藏和可解锁的拓展形态。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200 多个纯手K技能动画的深度回合制战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还可以使用积分招募美食精灵，而不是烹饪它们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由漫威和 DC 艺术家罗西·坎佩 创作的漫画作品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至多12 位美食角斗士同场竞技，大量独特联合技能与战术等你来探索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >附带 “酸甜苦辣”调味器的无尽肉鸽模式，让你吃到爽。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角斗士可解锁 2 种拓展外观！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/f252be1e961356cc2618e4ec545bf048.poster.avif?t=1771580853\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141280/extras/f252be1e961356cc2618e4ec545bf048.webm?t=1771580853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
